          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p>Rev. Sir</p>
                              <p>According to my promise I beg have to<lb/> give you a short sketch
                                        of the hebrew Congr<lb/> Beth Israel of this city.</p>
                              <p>The foundation of this Congr was laid about<lb/> 5 years ago by 6
                                        members, and has under the<lb/>
                                        <add>?</add> providence and guidance of the God of<lb/>
                                        <placeName>Israel</placeName> increased to the number of 50,
                                        of thriving<lb/> buisness and good standing in society. They
                                        meet<lb/> quarterly to transact business and
                                                  <sic>chose</sic> their<lb/> officer at their
                                        quart. Meeting <sic>holden</sic> during the<lb/>
                                        <add>חג</add> of <add>פסח</add>. The officers at present are
                                                  <persName>Mayer</persName><lb/>
                                        <persName>Stern</persName>, 1 Pres, <persName>Isac
                                                  Hartman</persName>, 2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> Pres.
                                                  <persName>Abr.<lb/>
                                                  Hallamler<add>?</add></persName> comtroller, and
                                                  <persName>Hirsh Wallach</persName><lb/> &amp;
                                                  <persName>Alex Rothschild</persName> Trustee.</p>
                              <p>The means of the Congr not being sufficient<lb/> to build a
                                        suitable house of prayer, the Congr<lb/> worship the God of
                                        their fathers, in a hall rented<lb/> and fitted up for that
                                        purpose; the reading of<lb/> the services is performed by
                                                  <add>?</add>
                                        <persName>M. L. Strauss</persName><lb/> who officiates as
                                                  <add>חזן</add> and <add>שוחט</add>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">There is here also a hebrew and english<lb/>
                                        school, and the number of scholars at present<lb/> is 25;
                                        they are under my care.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">With the <sic>greaters</sic> esteem</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">yours truly</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">
                                        <persName role="author">L Moscacher<add>?</add></persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>Hpd <date>13/9 51</date>.</p>
